nmap <tab> :tabn<Enter>
nmap <C-Right> :tabn<Enter>
nmap <C-Left> :tabN<Enter>

nmap <C-Tab> :tabN<Enter>
nmap <C-&> :tabn1<Enter>
nmap <C-é> :tabn2<Enter>
nmap <C-"> :tabn3<Enter>
nmap <C-'> :tabn4<Enter>


" Quickly edit/reload the vimrc file
nmap <silent> <leader>ev :e $MYVIMRC<CR>
nmap <silent> <leader>sv :so! $MYVIMRC<CR>
